<div id="about">
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Kickstart Buy One, Feed One on Campus</h2>
        <div id="students-intro">
        <p>Foodcircles is a website and mobile app that lets you feed a child in need by just eating out. We offer drinks, desserts, and appetizers at restaurants starting at $1. Every dollar spent is donated to feed hungry children.</p>
        <p>Starting Foodcircles in your area isn't paid, but with the good you'll be doing, the free swag you'll be getting, and the fun you'll be having it might feel like it! Check out the steps to starting FoodCircles and apply below.</p>
        </div>

